  "text": "The UpE MERS-CoV detection assay was used for the detection of MERS-CoV viral RNA [CITATION_1] . 5 ml RNA was tested with the Rotor-GeneTM probe kit (Qiagen) according to instructions of the manufacturer. Dilutions of MERS-CoV with known titer were run in parallel.",
